      "message": "This is critical required for StatefulSet Galera cluster. Without this DNS will not register the hostnames until the pods passes the readiness check. However to join the cluster these hostnames needs to be registered by DNS even if the readiness fails in order for the members to be able to nslookup themselvss and to join the cluster.",
